title: Salvador Dalí A Chemist Lifting with Extreme Precaution the Cuticle of a Grand Piano Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from Salvador Dalí’s, A Chemist Lifting with Extreme Precaution the Cuticle of a Grand Piano, 1936, from The Art Institute of Chicago’s collection. © Salvador Dalí, Fundació Gala- Salvador Dalí / Artists Rights Society (ARS), New York, 2022.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 2.5 in.
